trans-unit.source: Serves as a non-acting reader of incoming response return values for Web service clients implemented using HTTP but without SOAP.
trans-unit.target: Fungerer som ikke fungerer leseren av innkommende svar returnere verdier for Web service-klienter implementert ved hjelp av HTTP, men uten SOAP.

trans-unit.source: NopReturnReader and other classes in the <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols> namespace support the .NET Framework's implementations of Web services via the HTTP-GET and HTTP-POST operations.
trans-unit.target: NopReturnReader og andre klasser i den <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols>navneområdet støtter .NET Framework-implementeringer av webtjenester via HTTP-GET og HTTP-POST-operasjoner.</xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols>

trans-unit.source: Web service writers and readers serialize and deserialize, respectively, between the parameters or return objects of Web methods and the HTTP request or response streams.
trans-unit.target: Web service forfattere lesere serialisere og deserialisere henholdsvis mellom parameterne eller return objekter av Web-metoder og HTTP-forespørselen eller svar dataflytene.

trans-unit.source: Web service writers and readers use HTTP for transport but don't exchange messages using the SOAP standard.
trans-unit.target: Web service forfattere og lesere bruke HTTP til transport, men exchange ikke meldinger ved hjelp av SOAP-standard.

trans-unit.source: The NopReturnReader class provides a non-reading implementation of the interface of the abstract class <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.MimeReturnReader>.
trans-unit.target: Klassen NopReturnReader gir en ikke-lesing implementering av grensesnittet av den abstrakte klassen <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.MimeReturnReader>.</xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.MimeReturnReader>

trans-unit.source: You typically will not need to use the NopReturnReader class.
trans-unit.target: Du trenger vanligvis ikke å bruke NopReturnReader-klassen.

trans-unit.source: Instead, when the Wsdl.exe tool generates client proxy code according to the HTTP-GET or HTTP-POST implementations, .it applies the <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.HttpMethodAttribute> to each Web method and, by default, sets the attribute's <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.HttpMethodAttribute.ReturnFormatter%2A> property to <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.XmlReturnReader>, another class derived from <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.MimeReturnReader>.
trans-unit.target: I stedet når verktøyet Wsdl.exe genererer proxy-Klientkoden i henhold til implementeringer HTTP-GET eller HTTP-POST, gjelder .it <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.HttpMethodAttribute>til hver Web-metode, og som standard angir attributtets- <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.HttpMethodAttribute.ReturnFormatter%2A>egenskapen til <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.XmlReturnReader>en annen klasse som er avledet fra <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.MimeReturnReader>.</xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.MimeReturnReader> ,</xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.XmlReturnReader> </xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.HttpMethodAttribute.ReturnFormatter%2A> </xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.HttpMethodAttribute>

trans-unit.source: Wsdl.exe sets the property to NopReturnReader if it is otherwise unable to determine a value.
trans-unit.target: WSDL.exe egenskapen til NopReturnReader hvis den er ellers kan ikke fastsette en verdi.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Protocols.NopReturnReader"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Web.Services.Protocols.NopReturnReader"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: Returns an initializer for the specified method.
trans-unit.target: Returnerer en initialisering for den angitte metoden.

trans-unit.source: An initializer is an object passed as a parameter to the <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.NopReturnReader.Initialize%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: En initialisering er et objekt som ble sendt som en parameter i <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.NopReturnReader.Initialize%2A>metode.</xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.NopReturnReader.Initialize%2A>

trans-unit.source: For the <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.NopReturnReader> class, the initializer is the instance referred to by the keyword `this`.
trans-unit.target: For den <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.NopReturnReader>klassen, er initialiseringen forekomsten av referert til av nøkkelordet `this`.</xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.NopReturnReader>

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Web.Services.Protocols.LogicalMethodInfo"></xref> that specifies the Web method for which the initializer is obtained.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Web.Services.Protocols.LogicalMethodInfo"> </xref> som angir Web-metoden i initialisering hentes.

trans-unit.source: An initializer for the specified method.
trans-unit.target: En initialisering for den angitte metoden.

trans-unit.source: Initializes an instance.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en forekomst.

trans-unit.source: The Initialize method does nothing.
trans-unit.target: I initialiseringsmetoden gjøre noe.

trans-unit.source: It is invoked at the time a response is processed.
trans-unit.target: Den aktiveres på tidspunktet svar er behandlet.

trans-unit.source: The input parameter, `initializer`, is another instance of the class that is obtained during client initialization.
trans-unit.target: Inndataparameteren `initializer`, er en annen forekomst av klassen som er hentet under initialisering av klienten.

trans-unit.source: Another instance of the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Protocols.NopReturnReader"></xref> class, on which the <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.NopReturnReader.GetInitializer*> method was previously called.
trans-unit.target: En annen forekomst av den <xref href="System.Web.Services.Protocols.NopReturnReader"> </xref> klassen som den <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.NopReturnReader.GetInitializer*>metoden tidligere ble kalt.</xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.NopReturnReader.GetInitializer*>

trans-unit.source: Returns <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""></xref> instead of deserializing the HTTP response stream into a Web method return value.
trans-unit.target: Returnerer <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""> </xref> i stedet for deserialisering av HTTP-svar-dataflyten til en webmetode returverdi.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.NopReturnReader> class's implementation of the <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.MimeReturnReader.Read%2A> method does no reading.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.NopReturnReader>klassens implementering av <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.MimeReturnReader.Read%2A>metoden støtter ikke lesing.</xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.MimeReturnReader.Read%2A> </xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.NopReturnReader>

trans-unit.source: Instead it returns `null`.
trans-unit.target: Returnerer den i stedet `null`.

trans-unit.source: It also closes the response stream.
trans-unit.target: Lukker også svar-dataflyten.

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Net.WebResponse> object containing the output message for an operation.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.Net.WebResponse>objektet som inneholder utdatameldingen for en operasjon.</xref:System.Net.WebResponse>

trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.IO.Stream>filreferanser meldingsteksten i HTTP-svar representeres av den `response` parameteren.</xref:System.IO.Stream>
